Package com.flipkart.business

Interface GymOwnerServiceInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GymOwnerService
    public interface GymOwnerServiceInterface
    This interface defines the service operations related to Gym Owner functionality. It includes methods for requesting gym owner approval, viewing all gym owners, logging in gym owners, and registering new gym owners.
